        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "A creature with the pod-spawned template is a duplicate created by the bodythief. It resembles the original and has all its memories, but can\u2019t exhibit sincere emotion.<br/> Pod-spawned creatures can\u2019t reproduce and remain the same apparent age as their original at the time of replacement."
        }
